&lt;/form&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
```

Finally, update the `@PostMapping` like this:

```
@PostMapping(&quot;/play&quot;)
    public String checkPokemonSubmit(@ModelAttribute(&quot;answer&quot;) AnswerFormData answer, Model model) {

    // Compare answer.getName() with the name of the pokemon here
